Phase 6 - Operations and Monitoring
-----------------------------------

Security Activities
• Security monitoring
• Incident response
• Vulnerability management
• Patch management
• Security metrics and reporting

Tools & Technologies
• SIEM: Splunk, IBM QRadar, Azure Sentinel
• EDR: CrowdStrike, Carbon Black, SentinelOne
• Vulnerability scanners: Qualys, Tenable Nessus
• WAF: CloudFlare, AWS WAF, F5
• SOAR: Palo Alto Cortex XSOAR, Splunk SOAR

Methodologies & Standards
• Continuous security monitoring
• NIST Cybersecurity Framework
• Incident response playbooks
• Mean Time to Detect/Respond (MTTD/MTTR)
• Security KPI/KRI tracking

Key Deliverables
• Security dashboards
• Incident reports
• Vulnerability management reports
• Patch compliance reports
• Security posture assessments
